+
+  <!-- Setup Guide -->
+  <details>
+    <summary>Setup Guide</summary>
+    <div class="panel-body">
+      <p>Windows only routes audio to one output by default. To send audio to multiple speakers:</p>
+      <h3>Method 1: Stereo Mix (Built-in)</h3>
+      <ol>
+        <li>Right-click speaker icon &rarr; <code>Sounds</code></li>
+        <li><code>Recording</code> tab &rarr; right-click &rarr; <code>Show Disabled Devices</code></li>
+        <li>Enable <code>Stereo Mix</code></li>
+        <li>Properties &rarr; <code>Listen</code> &rarr; check <code>Listen to this device</code> &rarr; select secondary speaker</li>
